+   realization datum or exact coefficient identity later steps might want to
+   promote?
+   Separate promoted authority from draft helpers, provisional arithmetic,
+   runtime logs, or non-authoritative notes.
+5. What is the strongest honest maximum scope already licensed by the local
+   record for this chain step:
+   one single audited realization,
+   one explicitly parameterized audited family,
+   or only a scope-control / source-basis memo?
+   Explain why broader scope is not yet licensed.
+6. Based on the local record alone, what is the minimum honest Step-9
+   exploration split?
+   Are two explorations enough:
+   one inherited-ledger / freedom freeze and one realization-provenance / scope
+   audit,
+   or does the record force a third synthesis exploration?
+
