+For mission `exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit`, step `step-009`, identify
+the strongest local repository materials for freezing Chain Step 1 of the new
+run-003 chain:
+
+`Freeze The Inherited Ledger, Provenance Burden, Remaining Freedoms, And Claim Scope`
