+
+## Constraints
+
+- Do not do Chain Step 2 work.
+- Do not compute the full exact coefficient ledger.
+- Do not invent an explicit wavevector family or finite closure convention.
+- Use the inherited local record only.
+- Write `REPORT-SUMMARY.md` as the sentinel deliverable.
