+## Constraints
+
+- Do not do Chain Step 2 recursive closure work.
+- Do not create a new realization by convenience.
+- Do not use draft helpers as theorem authority.
+- If the explicit realization/provenance burden is not met, stop with the
+  negative memo instead of repairing it.
+- Write `REPORT-SUMMARY.md` as the sentinel deliverable.
